OL,3,CBurglar jailed over deadly attack on
OL,4,Cmother's 94-year-old neighbour
OL,6,FA burglar who targeted his mother's 94-
OL,7,Fyear-old neighbour and then subjected
OL,8,Fhim to a deadly attack has been jailed.
OL,10,FPaul Topham, 46, used stolen keys to
OL,11,Fenter Harold Monk's flat in Inglewood
OL,12,FAvenue in Wolverhampton, in the early
OL,13,Fhours of 3 October 2024.
OL,15,FWhen challenged about the intrusion,
OL,16,Fhe held down Mr Monk and repeatedly
OL,17,Fbeat him.
OL,19,FThe 94-year-old suffered fractures to
OL,20,Fhis face, skull, spine and ribs, and
OL,21,Fdied in hospital a day later.
