OL,3,CBurglar jailed over deadly attack on
OL,4,Cmother's 94-year-old neighbour
OL,6,FTopham, of Palmerston Road in
OL,7,FBirmingham, tried to deny murder but a
OL,8,Fjury found him guilty in July. He was
OL,9,Fsentenced on Thursday to life in
OL,10,Fprison with a minimum of 33 years.
OL,12,FThe court heard Topham visited his
OL,13,Fmother at the sheltered retirement
OL,14,Fblock the weekend before the attack.
OL,15,FHe stole Mr Monk's keys when he saw
OL,16,Fthem left in the door.
