OL,3,CBurglar jailed over deadly attack on
OL,4,Cmother's 94-year-old neighbour
OL,6,FA neighbour who heard the commotion
OL,7,Ffound Topham on top of Mr Monk. The
OL,8,Fneighbour called police after failing
OL,9,Fto intervene.
OL,11,FThe court heard Topham continued to
OL,12,Fburgle Mr Monk's flat while the
OL,13,Felderly man lay dying.
OL,15,FTopham was arrested after a short
OL,16,Fstandoff on a nearby roof.
OL,18,FMr Monk died in hospital the next day,
OL,19,Fon 4 October.
