OL,6,FHis daughter Patricia said in a
OL,7,Fstatement read out in court: "It broke
OL,8,Four hearts to see him lying there in
OL,9,Fthe bed his face battered covered in
OL,10,Fbruises and trying not to think of the
OL,11,Finternal injuries, we knew he was in
OL,12,Fpain."
OL,14,FShe continued: "Dad would have been 95
OL,15,Fyears old in November 2024 and he was
OL,16,Flooking forward to his forthcoming
OL,17,Fbirthday and had even decided he was
OL,18,Fhaving fish and chips as a celebration
OL,19,Fdinner.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/12
