OL,6,F"Christmas 2024 was particularly hard
OL,7,Fas he would always spend it with me
OL,8,Fsitting in his favourite chair,
OL,9,Fwatching his favourite programmes on
OL,10,Fthe television.
OL,12,F"It was Father's Day on 15th June 2025
OL,13,FI felt a mix of emotions, sadness, a
OL,14,Fsense of anger that I was unable to
OL,15,Fsend him a Father's Day card and huge
OL,16,Fsense of loss without him."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/12
