OL,6,FMr Monk leaves behind three children,
OL,7,Fsix grandchildren, 11 great-
OL,8,Fgrandchildren, and two great-great-
OL,9,Fgrandchildren.
OL,11,FHe has worked as a bookkeeper, at
OL,12,FMitchells and Butlers brewery, and at
OL,13,FGoodyear Tyres in Wolverhampton before
OL,14,Fretiring. He was described as being
OL,15,F"very active" during retirement.
OL,17,FHis family said he was "intelligent
OL,18,Fand astute and loved completing
OL,19,Fcrosswords and suduko and every night
OL,20,FheJwould complete the Express and Star
OL,21,Fcrossword".
