OL,3,CBurglar jailed over deadly attack on
OL,4,Cmother's 94-year-old neighbour
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Phil Poole said
OL,7,Fthe level of violence used against the
OL,8,F94-year-old man was 'absolutely
OL,9,Fdisproportionate'
OL,11,FSenior investigating officer DI Phil
OL,12,FPoole said the level of violence used
OL,13,Fagainst Mr Monk, who was
OL,14,F"defenceless", was "absolutely
OL,15,Fdisproportionate".
OL,17,FHe said: "Paul Topham had more than
OL,18,Fample opportunity to withdraw himself
OL,19,Ffrom that situation and chose not to,
OL,20,Fhe chose to go on to assault Harold,
OL,21,Fin a very callous and calculating way.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/12
