OL,6,F"Quite frankly, everybody on the
OL,7,Finvestigation team were appalled by
OL,8,Fwhat they saw."
OL,10,FA court heard Topham stole a key fob,
OL,11,Fglasses, enamel badges and paperwork
OL,12,Ffrom Mr Monk's home.
OL,14,FDI Poole said: "What was really clear
OL,15,Fwas that Paul Topham gave evidence in
OL,16,Fhis own defence, and he tried to
OL,17,Fminimise what he'd done and the impact
OL,18,Fthat had had, by suggesting he'd been
OL,19,Fsubjected to alcohol and drug
OL,20,Fintoxication.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/12
