OL,6,F"However we gathered evidence to
OL,7,Fdiscount or refute that. When we saw
OL,8,FPaul Topham on CCTV on his journey
OL,9,Ffrom Birmingham to Wolverhampton, it
OL,10,Fwas clear that he was a man on a
OL,11,Fmission."
OL,13,FHe continued: "Paul Topham has shown
OL,14,Fzero remorse for what he's done, the
OL,15,Ftears that were seen in court, I
OL,16,Fthink, were self pity and not a
OL,17,Freflection of the impact he's had on
OL,18,FHarold and Harold's family."
